<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Coffee 99 - Nikmati Kopi Terbaik</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <header class="hero-section text-white d-flex align-items-center"
        style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), url('/image/hero-bg.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover; height: 80vh; margin-top: 90px;">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h1 class="display-2 fw-bold mb-3">Awali Harimu dengan <span style="color: var(--accent-gold);">Kopi
                    Sempurna</span></h1>
            <p class="lead mb-4">Biji kopi pilihan, dipanggang dengan cinta, disajikan untuk menginspirasi setiap
                langkahmu.</p>
            <a href="/products" class="btn btn-lg btn-success px-5 py-3 fw-bold shadow">LIHAT MENU SEKARANG</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="about" class="py-5 bg-white">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row text-center g-4">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-leaf fa-3x mb-3" style="color: var(--primary-coffee);"></i>
                        <h4>Biji Kopi Organik</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">Kami hanya menggunakan biji kopi pilihan dari petani lokal terbaik.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-4 border-start border-end">
                        <i class="fas fa-bolt fa-3x mb-3" style="color: var(--primary-coffee);"></i>
                        <h4>Proses Cepat</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">Pesananmu akan diproses segera setelah pembayaran dikonfirmasi.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-medal fa-3x mb-3" style="color: var(--primary-coffee);"></i>
                        <h4>Kualitas Premium</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">Rasa konsisten yang telah memikat ribuan pecinta kopi di Indonesia.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="locations" class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
                <h2 class="fw-bold">Lokasi Coffee 99</h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Temukan outlet terdekat dan nikmati kopi favoritmu.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row g-4 align-items-stretch">
                <div class="col-lg-7">
                    <div class="location-map-shell">
                        <iframe
                            title="Peta Lokasi Coffee 99"
                            src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Jakarta%20Selatan&t=&z=10&ie=UTF8&iwloc=&output=embed"
                            loading="lazy"
                            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
                            allowfullscreen
                        ></iframe>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5">
                    <div class="location-list-panel">
                        <div class="location-item">
                            <div class="location-item-head">
                                <i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill"></i>
                                <h5 class="mb-0">Jakarta Selatan</h5>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-2">Jl. Panglima Polim No. 12, Jakarta Selatan</p>
                            <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Jl.+Panglima+Polim+No.+12,+Jakarta+Selatan" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Buka di Google Maps</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="location-item">
                            <div class="location-item-head">
                                <i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill"></i>
                                <h5 class="mb-0">Bekasi</h5>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-2">Jl. Ahmad Yani No. 88, Bekasi</p>
                            <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Jl.+Ahmad+Yani+No.+88,+Bekasi" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Buka di Google Maps</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="location-item">
                            <div class="location-item-head">
                                <i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill"></i>
                                <h5 class="mb-0">Tangerang</h5>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-2">Jl. BSD Raya Utama No. 5, Tangerang</p>
                            <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Jl.+BSD+Raya+Utama+No.+5,+Tangerang" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Buka di Google Maps</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-dark text-white py-4 mt-5">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <p class="mb-0">&copy; 2026 Coffee 99. Dibuat dengan <i class="fas fa-heart text-danger"></i> oleh Mahasiswa
                IT UBJ.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
